Stronghold and Blender both fall from the shots. Burning Hammer starts
prying Serge's mouth open with the scissors. (Alot of strength) Until he
pried Inzola out. Inzola is about to thank him when she sees Stranato in a
very large pool of mech fluid. While she rushes to his side, Testifier
lunges forward (He was guarding Deemos' back) And takes all of the missile.
Deemos growls and starts slicing into Psuedo...

at

>
> The Alliance bot lowers altitude, flying behind Deemos, and shooting two

Psuedo
> would be hit or not, because Psuedo wasn't an Alliance bot, but if Deemos
> blocked with Psuedo, he'd be caught in the blast also.
>
> Having fired the two missiles, Reptilica flies back up, seeing the
Predacons
> retreating. He opens his comm-link. "Hey, Preds," he says into it, sending
it
> on a Predacon frequency, "What are you doing? Zardus didn't send us here
to
> whoop these Maxi's singlehandedly, ya know, ya gotta help."
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Bloodystrike flies in behind Stronghold, DevilDuer coming up behind
Blender.
> The two Alliance bots open fire on the two Maximals, aiming for their
heads.
